<title>SWITZERLAND: Swiss share market closed for Ascension holiday.</title>
<headline>Swiss share market closed for Ascension holiday.</headline>
<text>
<p>1120 GMT - The Swiss share market is closed on Thursday for Ascension Day holiday.</p>
<p>Trading will resume on Friday.</p>
<p>On Wednesday the blue-chip SMI index rose 27.6 points, or 0.55 percent, to close at 5,016.0. -- Zurich Newsroom +41 1 631 7342</p>
